Description: Weather app [using commandline] it takes location from user as a string using command line and then use that location to get GEOCODE of that 
particular place using MAPBOX API after that it uses darkshy.net API to get weather of that location.

Commands to RUN:
1. node app.js location         //if name is consist of single word like Paris
2. node app.js "location"       //if name consist of multiple words like "New York"

IMPORTANT NOTE
Before Running App type command "npm install" to fetch npm-modules required for running the app.
